TestDirectGoalCycleThrows
/ A goal that calls itself directly throws CallStackOverflowException — caught via ContainsGoal on Push. Wrap in error.handle so the test goal still completes.
- call TestDirectGoalCycleThrows, on error set %cycleCaught% = true
- assert %cycleCaught% is true, "self-recursive goal.call must trip ContainsGoal cycle detection"
